 {\"ngram\": \"young Caeleb\", \"from\": 8622, \"to\": 8634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel went to Tokyo with a six-race program, choosing an ambitious-but-manageable Olympics over an attempt at replicating Mark Spitz\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s seven golds in 1972 or Phelps\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 record eight in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009908.\", \"from\": 8637, \"to\": 8831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8653, \"end\": 8658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 2.028924920770292e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 8637, \"to\": 8644}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-race program\", \"from\": 8664, \"to\": 8682}, {\"ngram\": \"an ambitious-but-manageable Olympics\", \"from\": 8693, \"to\": 8729}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 8735, \"to\": 8745}, {\"ngram\": \"Mark\", \"from\": 8761, \"to\": 8765}, {\"ngram\": \"Phelps\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 record\", \"from\": 8799, \"to\": 8815}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009908\", \"from\": 8825, \"to\": 8830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won five, breaking his own world record in the 100 fly.\", \"from\": 8832, \"to\": 8890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own world record\", \"from\": 8854, \"to\": 8874}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 fly\", \"from\": 8878, \"to\": 8889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only miss was in the mixed medley relay, which was more a factor of lineup mismanagement than anything Dressel or the other swimmers did wrong in the water.\", \"from\": 8891, \"to\": 9051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only miss\", \"from\": 8891, \"to\": 8904}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed medley relay\", \"from\": 8912, \"to\": 8934}, {\"ngram\": \"more a factor\", \"from\": 8946, \"to\": 8959}, {\"ngram\": \"lineup mismanagement\", \"from\": 8963, \"to\": 8983}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"f