s\", \"from\": 10120, \"to\": 10139}, {\"ngram\": \"camera\", \"from\": 10159, \"to\": 10165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the moments you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t see.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Joy and satisfaction radiated at that point.\", \"from\": 10167, \"to\": 10251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10207, \"end\": 10210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.36029761882486e-35, \"text\": \"Joy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 10174, \"to\": 10185}, {\"ngram\": \"satisfaction\", \"from\": 10214, \"to\": 10226}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 10239, \"to\": 10249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or so we thought.\", \"from\": 10252, \"to\": 10269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t until later that we learned Dressel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s five-gold Olympics was considered flawed by the perfectionist himself.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI did not hit any of my goal times in Tokyo,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Dresselsaid in a 2022 interviewwithPeople.\", \"from\": 10270, \"to\": 10488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10436, \"end\": 10441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 2.028924920770292e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10310, \"to\": 10321}, {\"ngram\": \"five-gold Olympics\", \"from\": 10322, \"to\": 10340}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfectionist\", \"from\": 10366, \"to\": 10383}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 10392, \"to\": 10398}, {\"ngram\": \"my goal times\", \"from\": 10418, \"to\": 10431}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2022 interviewwithPeople\", \"from\": 10460, 