irst round\", \"from\": 11428, \"to\": 11443}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 freestyle\", \"from\": 11447, \"to\": 11464}, {\"ngram\": \"qualified second\", \"from\": 11469, \"to\": 11485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he abruptly withdrew from the event and eventually dropped out of the meet, citing a medical situation.\", \"from\": 11511, \"to\": 11619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 11542, \"to\": 11551}, {\"ngram\": \"the meet\", \"from\": 11582, \"to\": 11590}, {\"ngram\": \"a medical situation\", \"from\": 11599, \"to\": 11618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This marked the start of the disappearance.\\u00c2 Dressel has never explained what happened in Budapest.\", \"from\": 11621, \"to\": 11721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11712, \"end\": 11720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3706270986858694e-26, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 11633, \"to\": 11642}, {\"ngram\": \"the disappearance\", \"from\": 11646, \"to\": 11663}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Dressel\", \"from\": 11664, \"to\": 11673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His coach, Anthony Nesty, alluded in 2023 to a mental health issue, and that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s about it.\", \"from\": 11722, \"to\": 11812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11733, \"end\": 11746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Nesty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His coach\", \"from\": 11722, \"to\": 11731}, {\"ngram\": \"a mental health issue\", \"from\": 11767, \"to\": 11788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a testament to h