e2\\u0080\\u009d In August 2022, Dressel posted an advertisement for his suit sponsor, Speedo, on Instagram.\", \"from\": 12213, \"to\": 12416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12395, \"end\": 12401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.642002825209104e-35, \"text\": \"Speedo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speedo\"}, {\"begin\": 12406, \"end\": 12415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6158086893843523e-67, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 12247, \"to\": 12253}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a while\", \"from\": 12278, \"to\": 12291}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 12327, \"to\": 12333}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 12340, \"to\": 12347}, {\"ngram\": \"an advertisement\", \"from\": 12355, \"to\": 12371}, {\"ngram\": \"his suit sponsor\", \"from\": 12376, \"to\": 12392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A month later he posted something in his own words on what he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d been up to while out of the pool.\", \"from\": 12417, \"to\": 12516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 12441, \"to\": 12450}, {\"ngram\": \"his own words\", \"from\": 12454, \"to\": 12467}, {\"ngram\": \"he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 12476, \"to\": 12482}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 12507, \"to\": 12515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI finally went on a honeymoon to Iceland, I bought a tractor, hiked another section of the Appalachian Trail, swam with some manatees.\", \"from\": 12517, \"to\": 12654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12553, \"end\": 12560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iceland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 1.8